title: 30 Min CALISTHENICS WORKOUT | No Equipment | DAY 1
description:
Ready for Day 1 of my Calisthenics series? This is a 30 minute Calisthenics workout with no equipment needed you can follow along at home. This routine is designed to build muscle, increase strength and develop flexibility. The full body workout includes beginner Calisthenics exercises, as well as more advanced variations making it suitable for a range of abilities.
